{"tid":1202584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［unwire.hk] 【教學】去野餐防洩露行蹤　前偵探教你 18 個必學防被追蹤技","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T10:03:55.000Z","uid":33307,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"830dc251f53d4b165c570b603f2d48667181991c","tid":1202584,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"近年筆者經常聽聞有些人明明沒有公開說甚麼，但偏偏就有人監聽到；有些人去一些地方或者做一些活動，例如去公園野餐，但就有人知道他們的行蹤。其實在今日這個智能年代，如果不小心一點，你說甚麼、去過哪裡、做過甚麼，也有可能透過你隨身的裝置，在不知不覺之間洩漏出去，讓有心人可以監聽或者跟蹤到。如果不想行蹤那麼容易被洩漏，我們就專訪了以前從事私家商業偵探的華哥（化名），讓他向大家透露一些他們常用多種追蹤手法，以及如何防守吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/11/8-prevent-location-leaking-skills-tutorial/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F8-prevent-location-leaking-skills-tutorial%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9989b6fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/11/8-prevent-location-leaking-skills-tutorial/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"47553c4d06f3cb26f8c954d3f45e3e49b7e4898a","tid":1202584,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e757dde6c9e0853a69d050e2ca468031afaf6d1b","tid":1202584,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfa703369eacea4428f9063035808b40c5675b7","tid":1202584,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1ac5e86e29508170ebee82f832408c2fd47f0f","tid":1202584,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f162f6e8e5707099169bb1c2827309f544